  ('antena-satelitska-sr-mecatronic-asr650-flat-led-gold-edition', 'Antena satelitska SR Mecatronic ASR650 Flat LED GOLD EDITION', null, 'Satelitska antena SR Mecatronic ASR 650 Flat Gold Edition s dvostrukim iluminatorom i Bluetooth vezom.

